description: Removes a tag or tags from a resource.

parameters.name: ResourceArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource that you want to untag.

parameters.name: TagKeys
parameters.description: The keys of the key-value pairs for the resource tag or tags assigned to the resource. (string) ---

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.
